org.apache.beam.runners.dataflow.options

Interface DataflowWorkerHarnessOptions

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ApplicationNameOptions, BigQueryOptions, CloudDebuggerOptions, DataflowPipelineDebugOptions, DataflowPipelineOptions, DataflowPipelineWorkerPoolOptions, DataflowProfilingOptions, DataflowWorkerLoggingOptions, ExperimentalOptions, GcpOptions, GcsOptions, GoogleApiDebugOptions, HasDisplayData, PipelineOptions, PubsubOptions, StreamingOptions

    @Hidden
public interface DataflowWorkerHarnessOptions
extends DataflowPipelineOptions
    Options that are used exclusively within the Dataflow worker harness. These options have no effect at pipeline creation time.
